docs.text:
Welcome to Vaex-docs


Introduction


Welcome to the Vaex API! You can use our API to create machine learning pipeline in 10th of the time, ready for production. We aim to empower data scientists to work on exploration, cleaning, and modeling, all the way to production without changing APIs, and technologies.


We have language bindings Python, and a CLI for some common tasks we wanted to automate.


Mkdocs




mkdocs new [dir-name]
 - Create a new project.


mkdocs serve
 - Start the live-reloading docs server.


mkdocs build
 - Build the documentation site.


mkdocs help
 - Print this help message.




Installation


clone...
python setup install
